column1: In case of problem, please report to:
<DESCRIPTION>Simbad column added by the CDS [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<!-- Original table number: {\bf4}=sources with higexcitation emission of [OIII], {\bf10}-{\bf11}=sources with high S/N, {\bf 12}=sources with lower (<10) S/N -->
<DESCRIPTION>[io] inner or outer region of NGC 6822</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="RAJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.ra;meta.main" ref="J2000" datatype="double" width="10" precision="6" unit="deg"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_RA_MAIN" -->
<FIELD name="DEJ2000" ucd="pos.eq.dec;meta.main" ref="J2000" datatype="double" width="10" precision="6" unit="deg"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_DEC_MAIN" -->
<FIELD name="Jmag" ucd="phot.mag;em.IR.J" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_J" -->
<FIELD name="Hmag" ucd="phot.mag;em.IR.H" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_H" -->
<FIELD name="Kmag" ucd="phot.mag;em.IR.K" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_JHN_K" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[*] * for rejected from the photometric sample in Paper I (3)</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="Dist" ucd="pos.distance;pos.galactocentric" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="kpc"><!-- ucd="POS_GAL_GC" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[1/900]? Identification number in Letarte et al. 2002 (J/AJ/123/832) [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="R-I" ucd="phot.color;em.opt.R;em.opt.I" datatype="float" width="6" precision="3" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_CI_R-I" -->
<FIELD name="CN-TiO" ucd="phot.color;em.opt.I;em.opt.I" datatype="float" width="6" precision="3" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_CI_CN-TIO" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Data from Paper I (Sibbons et al. 2012, Cat. J/A+A/540/A135)</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="recno" ucd="meta.record" datatype="int" width="8" type="hidden"><!-- ucd="RECORD" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Record number assigned by the VizieR team. Should Not be used for identification.</DESCRIPTION>
